#NOP  FAITH ROD CHARGE LEVELS:
#NOP
#NOP =============================================
#NOP
#NOP   INDEX:
#NOP
#NOP   Part 1: Variable declaration.
#NOP
#NOP   Part 2: Code for Priest characters.
#NOP
#NOP   Part 3: Code for non-Priest characters.
#NOP
#NOP =============================================
#NOP
#NOP
#NOP =============================================
#NOP
#NOP PART 1: VARIABLES:
#NOP
#VARIABLE {TTMod_Reset} {<088>}
#VARIABLE {TTMod_Blank} {<abc><AAA>}
#VARIABLE {TTMod_Current} {<FBA><fba>}
#VARIABLE {Rod_Part} {<088><fdc>}
#VARIABLE {Rod_Ritual} {<088><adf>}
#VARIABLE {Rod_Imbued} {<FFA>}
#VARIABLE {Rod_Impressed} {<AFA>}
#VARIABLE {Rod_Imprinted} {<ADF>}
#NOP
#NOP PART 2: PRIESTS:
#NOP
#NOP  $TTMod_Current indicates current charge level.
#NOP
#NOP  $Rod_Imbued indicates rod is so far up to imbued level.
#NOP    The ritual can be used once, but it will be lost.
#NOP
#NOP  $Rod_Impressed indicates rod is so far up to impressed level.
#NOP    The ritual can be used many times, so long as the rod is not reconsecrated.
#NOP
#NOP  $Rod_Imprinted indicates rod has been fully imprinted.
#NOP    The ritual can be used many times, and would survive reconsecration.
#NOP
#NOP EMPTY
#SUBSTITUTE
  {The %1 {is|are} empty and {is|are} linked to the %2.}
  {  %2 \\ $Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[]\t[$TTMod_Blank       |       $TTMod_Reset]}
#SUBSTITUTE
  {The %1 {is|are} empty and {is|are} not dependent on any other part of the %2.}
  { $Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[]\t[$TTMod_Blank       |       $TTMod_Reset]}
#NOP
#NOP IMBUED 1
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} linked to the %3.  {It glows|They glow} with a barely visible light.}
  {   %3\\$Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$TTMod_Current $TTMod_Blank      |       $TTMod_Reset]}
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} not dependent on any other part of %3.  {It glows|They glow} with a barely visible light.}
  { $Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$TTMod_Current $TTMod_Blank      |       $TTMod_Reset]}
#NOP
#NOP IMBUED 2
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} linked to the %3.  {It glows|They glow} with a faint light.}
