#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} not dependent on any other part of %3.  {It glows|They glow} with a faint light.}
  { $Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$Rod_Imbued $TTMod_Current $TTMod_Blank     |       $TTMod_Reset]}
#NOP
