#NOP IMPRESSED 1
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} impressed with the ritual %2 and {is|are} linked to the %3.  {It glows|They glow} with a softly pulsing light.}
  {   %3\\$Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$Rod_Impressed       |$TTMod_Current $TTMod_Blank      $TTMod_Reset]}
