#NOP =============================================
#NOP
#NOP PART 3: NON-PRIESTS
#NOP
#NOP  $TTMod_Current indicates rod is being imbued or impressed.
#NOP
#NOP  $Rod_Impressed means rod has been imbued completely, but is not yet imprinted.
#NOP
#NOP  $Rod_Imprinted mean rod has been fully imprinted.
#NOP
#NOP IMBUED
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} linked to the %3.$}
  {   %3\\$Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$TTMod_Current       $TTMod_Blank|       $TTMod_Reset]}
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} imbued with the ritual %2 and {is|are} not dependent on any other part of the %3.$}
  { $Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$TTMod_Current       $TTMod_Blank|       $TTMod_Reset]}
#NOP
#NOP IMPRESSED
#SUBSTITUTE
  {^The %1 {is|are} impressed with the ritual %2 and {is|are} linked to the %3.$}
  {   %3\\$Rod_Part %1$TTMod_Reset\t[$Rod_Ritual %2 $TTMod_Reset]\t[$TTMod_Blank$Rod_Imbued       |$TTMod_Current       $TTMod_Reset]}
